---
title: Spring Tortellini Gratin with Asparagus and Parmesan Breadcrumbs
description: This skillet pasta bake truly is a one-pot-wonder – the creamy pesto sauce thickens in the pan while the tortellini cook! A crispy topping of panko and Parmesan goes under the broiler for a few minutes until bubbly, browned, and irresistible.
